{"tid":1123612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【九子判刑】黃照達更新佔中標誌 「籠外鳥」回應裁決","createTime":"2019-04-24T14:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T17:15:09.000Z","uid":140831,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19d548a4dea03eb7c22c88bbc5594fddf9f4c985","tid":1123612,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kKRrCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kKRrCk.png&h=6b0c77a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著佔中九子今日判刑，其中四名被告即時入獄，佔中標誌設計者黃照達今日下午在 Facebook 上傳該標誌的「更新版」&mdash;&mdash;原本中空的圓形已加上欄柵，像是牢籠，但小雀依然站在圓上，站在籠外，仰望天空。黃照達亦留言道：「向每位為香港民主付出過的致敬」。<br />\n<br />\n政治漫畫家黃照達 2013 年為和平佔中運動設計標誌&mdash;&mdash;一隻小雀站在中空的圓形上。乍看之下，小雀顯得有點微弱、孤單，但當年黃照達談及設計理念時曾寫到：「至於雀，雖然微小，卻是從容的，堅定的，站在圓上，不用佔領，因牠本已自由。」黃照達新上傳的相片中，佔中標誌原本留白的圓心，卻填上了一條條直線，像是監獄牢房的門。然而，那道門後並沒有困住任何東西，那自由的小雀依舊站在圓上，從容而堅定。<br />\n<br />\n黃照達在帖子寫到：「向每位為香港民主付出過的致敬」。有人留言感謝黃照達的設計：「留下的圓圈是個問號、是未完成的事、是未知的答案，是包容和虛弱，也是擁抱和強壯。」而黃照達亦指佔中標誌是自己至今最喜歡和最重要的作品。 黃照達現為浸大視覺藝術學院講師，也是一名政治漫畫家，希望透過漫畫去抒解對社會的不安與憤怒。"},{"pid":"f1a46ca5c9abd8ae2325c65a85e58a43bb6aa4cc","tid":1123612,"uid":140831,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"好靚好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻覺得香港再次有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae535c6d327aec8a9d488107e31d2d6fcba91bb","tid":1123612,"uid":28181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"雷動之後就係風雲計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ef70j05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fef70j05.png&h=e349c5e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16f546cd2bec2951b2a005e4fd456dca5e5f8137","tid":1123612,"uid":250048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"好撚感動呀，咪又係攞黎出product呃黃屍錢"},{"pid":"658cc69572bd8fcc113e156ee6710ae896221705","tid":1123612,"uid":140831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16f546cd2bec2951b2a005e4fd456dca5e5f8137","tid":1123612,"uid":250048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"好撚感動呀，咪又係攞黎出product呃黃屍錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"愛與和平 民主建中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8009fd3a6953c88fa66806835cf0c0c708b92ed","tid":1123612,"uid":25754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"皇上萬歲,大亨好犀利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 睇錯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efb3582c09608f2ff433ff8007e5ef2d50813ce","tid":1123612,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8009fd3a6953c88fa66806835cf0c0c708b92ed","tid":1123612,"uid":25754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"皇上萬歲,大亨好犀利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 睇錯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"唔好將和平建港鬥士同d搞亂香港既爛仔相提並論"},{"pid":"90a057e3d025a6cbaf3c81b2a6f86ff9396fd1c5","tid":1123612,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550a9080193455586ae416796e98495dc67b00cf","tid":1123612,"uid":62850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"有咗哩個新logo<br />\n香港有救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d67667e9216fced42f3e220028cb81c3c48e506","tid":1123612,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550a90801